1.01.name: wordpress/wp-flash-countdown
1.01.description: We present you a premium wordpress plugin which will enhance your webpage. Wordpress flash countdown allows you to display a countdown on your page. Or if you have a coming soon page it will display when it will be launched. It can be a perfect landing page for un upcoming website. A live example of the widget: http://premiumcoding.com/wordpress-count-down
